### Test Stats API
### Thay YOUR_JWT_TOKEN bằng token thực tế của student

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 1. Get Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Streak
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/streak
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Activity (Month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/activity?period=month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Activity (Week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/activity?period=week
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Activity (Year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/activity?period=year
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Category Distribution
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/category-distribution
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Weekly Activity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/weekly-activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Course Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/course-progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
